sequenceDiagram
  participant Cliente as Partner / script
  participant Auth as GET /authorize v1
  participant API as Rutas /api/shield/v1
  participant MW as shieldAuth.middleware

  Note over Auth,MW: authorize: GET /api/shield/v1/auth/authorize · middleware en todas las rutas

  Cliente->>Auth: Header x-api-key = API key del canal
  Auth-->>Cliente: 200 + JWT HS256<br/>subject = channel id
  Cliente->>API: Authorization Bearer JWT
  API->>MW: Verifica JWT con AUTH_SECRET
  MW->>API: Inyecta x-channel-id<br/>desde subject
  API-->>Cliente: Recurso risk items / policies
